unittitle_ssm: The Alfred Olcott Collection of Hudson River Steamboats
abstract_ssm: This collection contains photographs, ship plans and blueprints, ephemera, and clippings relating to Hudson River steamboats from the late-nineteenth to the mid-twentieth century.
subject_ssm: River steamers -- Hudson River (N.Y. and N.J.)
